Destroy weapon racks at Matum Graz

The watch-post of Matum Graz overlooks the path to the tower of Barad-dûr. Within the shattered walls of Matum Graz, forces of evil prepare to do battle with the forces of the Great Alliance. You should destroy the weapon-stores at Matum Graz and hinder these efforts.
Matum Graz can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should destroy weapon racks at Matum Graz.
Destroyed many weapons racks at Matum Graz.
